            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Here lies Ioannes, (son) of Georgios, (son) of Alexandros, who lived 60 years and
                    died on the 26th (day) of the month Daisios, on (the) day of (the) Lord Friday,
                    in the year 502, in the 10th indiction Christ, give him rest.</p>
